---
title: Moroccan-Style Bulgur Salad with Roasted Squash
description: Prepare for an explosion of tastes and colours with this hearty veggie grain salad. Moroccan-spiced roasted squash and harissa onions bring robust, fiery flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/freekeh-aux-epices-a-la-marocaine-58234629.jpg
